Subject: [PATCH 055/172] FogBugz #97184: Add Altera SYSID soft IP driver

This is to add Altera System ID (sysid) soft IP driver.
Usage:
cat /sys/bus/platform/devices/[addr].sysid/sysid/id
cat /sys/bus/platform/devices/[addr].sysid/sysid/timestamp

Signed-off-by: Ley Foon Tan <lftan@altera.com>
[czou:Original patch taken from
https://github.com/altera-opensource/linux-socfpga.git socfpga-4.1]
Signed-off-by: czou <cao.zou@windriver.com>
